{
  "stem": "964.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Didn't have enough bread.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And having a seder, in particular, without a father.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Passover-- we, we, we, we, we had the seder, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's what it is, but it a short-- a short-- not like a traditional seder, like other people had in those days.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Short seder, they just keep up the tradition.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We ate matzohs and those kind of things.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went to public school four years.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there, it was like-- in the public school, they used to give us-- since I was hungry.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was going around hung-- I was hungry-- so in the public school, when you went in the morning, they gave you a glass of milk and a roll of bread.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I got beaten up every day because I was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And was the-- it was the, the, the, the question, do you go to school or you don't go to school?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If you go to school, you get the bread and milk.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And if you don't go, you go hungry.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I had no choice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I had to go to school.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But every day in school was, was a, a-- was a-- I hate it, because you were beaten up.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And if you went to, to the-- to the principal, he said, you don't like it, go to Israel.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I would gladly go to Israel, but who, who, who-- the English didn't let us in.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Oh-- so we-- Eventually when I grow old-- I got older, in the same house where we lived, a Jewish guy had a, a,a factory of the cigarette pieces.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Not with-- without, without the tobacco.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Later on, you had to stick it, push in the tobacco.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So he employed me half a day, so I made 50 groszy, like $0.50.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
